  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf;\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "What is China's response to Samantha Bavary's comment on Sri Lanka's debt crisis?",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Spokesperson of the Chinese Ministry of Foreign Affairs, Zhao Lijian, said that Sri Lanka-China cooperation always follows Sri Lanka-led and Sri Lankan policies.",
        "He said this while responding to a question raised by reporters about USAIT's CEO Samantha Power's comments.",
        "He mentioned that all cooperation projects have been carried out on the basis of complete scientific research and thorough evaluations and said that no political conditions have been imposed.",
        "Chinese Foreign Ministry Spokesperson Zhao Lijian said that Sri Lankan Chinese cooperation has contributed to Sri Lankan economy and provided significant benefits to Sri Lankan people.",
        "He said that Sri Lanka's foreign debt has many components and China's contribution to Sri Lanka's debt is less than that of the international capital market multilateral development banks.",
        "He also said that China is providing preferential loans with low interest rates and long term maturity to Sri Lanka which has helped to enrich Sri Lanka's infrastructure and livelihood.",
        "He further stated that after Sri Lanka announced that it would stop issuing international loan payments, Chinese financial institutions approached the Sri Lankan side to find appropriate ways to deal with China-related maturing loans and to get rid of the crisis."
      ],
